function App() {
  return (
      <Router>
        <Header />
        <Switch>
          <Route path="/tv">
            <Tv />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/search">
            <Search />
          </Route>
          <Route path={["/", "/movies/:movieId"]}>
            <Home />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
      </Router>
  );
}

export default App
